VALUES('Yeezy Boost 700', 'Adidas', 'Inertia', 300, 'Add heavy pressure on your favorite sneakerhead and cop the adidas Yeezy Boost 700 Inertia. This Yeezy Boost 700 comes with a grey upper, grey midsole with orange accents, and a white sole. These sneakers released in March 2019 and retailed for $300.', 2019, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551991286&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Lv2/img28.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551991286&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551991286&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-700-Inertia/Lv2/img10.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551991286&w=1300');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Ultra Boost 2.0 ATR', 'Adidas', 'Glow in the Dark', 180, 'Adidas released this glow-in-the-dark edition of the Ultra Boost 2.0 ATR in September 2016. Sitting on a white Boost midsole, the performance runner sports a two-tone design that utilizes a mixture of grey and yellow coloring on the Primeknit upper. Those same hues are used individually on the midfoot cage and heel counter. The understated design takes on a new look when the lights go down, featuring neon-yellow glow-in-the-dark elements on the toe box and heel counter.', 2016, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Images/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Images/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Images/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Lv2/img14.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Images/Adidas-Ultra-Boost-ATR-Glow-In-The-Dark_TruView/Lv2/img07.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Yeezy 500 Salt', 'Adidas', 'Salt', 200, 'Don’t be salty, get out of your feelings, and cop a pair of the adidas Yeezy 500 Salt. With the potential of being the best Yeezy 500 colorway, these come with a salt upper, a salt midsole, and a salt sole.', 2018, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1544024798&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Lv2/img27.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1544024798&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1544024798&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-500-Salt/Lv2/img11.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1544024798&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Yeezy Boost 350 v2', 'Adidas', 'Cream White', 220, 'Does cash rule everything around you? If so, then it would be wise to cop the adidas Yeezy Boost 350 Cream White. Returning for round two with a huge restock, the luminous colored Yeezy Boost 350 has a cream white upper, core white midsole, and a camouflaged “SPLY-350” branding across the stripe on the sides.', 2017, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1539789713&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Lv2/img26.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1539789713&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Lv2/img21.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1539789713&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Images/Adidas-Yeezy-Boost-350-V2-Cream-White/Lv2/img08.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1539789713&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Solar', 'Adidas', 'Hu Pharrell Chinese New Year', 150, 'The Spring Festival is here, so cop the new adidas Solar Hu Pharrell Chinese New Year (2019). This Solar Hu comes with a red upper plus black and gold accents, white midsole, and black sole. These sneakers released in January 2019 and retailed for $150. Make Pharrell proud and cop these on StockX today.', 2019, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Images/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549854774&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Images/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Lv2/img31.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549854774&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Images/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549854774&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Images/Adidas-Solar-Hu-Pharrell-Chinese-New-Year-2019/Lv2/img10.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549854774&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Ultra Boost 1.0', 'Adidas', 'Wood Wood Black', 180, 'As part of adidas’ 2016 Consortium world tour, Danish streetwear brand Wood Wood’s Ultra Boost 1.0 design is inspired by scientist’s detection of gravitational waves in the afterglow of the Big Bang. The last untested prediction of Einstein’s theory of relativity finds its way into this black Primeknit.', 2016, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Images/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Images/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Images/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Lv2/img13.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Images/adidas-ultra-boost-wood-wood-black_TruView/Lv2/img08.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('ZX 4000 4D Carbon', 'Adidas', 'Carbon/Semi Solar Yellow', 350, 'As a nod to the ’80s ZX running shoes, adidas gave their ZX 4000 a modernized makeover with the debut of the adidas ZX 4000 4D, which debuts on February 9th.Adding to its lineup, the Three Stripes will be releasing an upcoming “Carbon” colorway. The shoe comes crafted in a knit upper with suede overlays keeping true to the original design updated with a digitally-printed midsole.', 2019, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Images/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551111806&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Images/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Lv2/img24.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551111806&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Images/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Lv2/img19.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551111806&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Images/Adidas-ZX-4000-4D-Carbon/Lv2/img07.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551111806&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel-Lyte 3.1 Ronnie Fieg', 'Asics', 'Salmon', 2016, 'Released as part of the ‘Legends Day’ pack in November 2016, the Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 3.1 "Salmon" features a salmon-colored premium pigskin suede upper with white accents on the medial toe. Other details include a Kith 5-Year logo on the heel, three additional lace options, a white midsole with visible blue Gel technology, and a light grey outsole.', 2016, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Lv2/img12.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-3pt1-ronnie-fieg-salmon_TruView/Lv2/img06.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel-Lyte 3 Afew x Beams', 'Asics', 'Orange Koi', 211, 'The collaboration between German footwear retailers Afew is a fitting tribute to the 25th anniversary of the Asics Gel Lyte III. The limited edition sneaker comes in full battle gear from the Bento box packaging, the design accents, and colorways, and the Japanese-inspired freebies included in each pair. What further makes this $180 per pair shoe much coveted is its limited edition status with only close to 2000 copies produced with many sneaker fans wanting this kicks in their collection', 2018, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546586103&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Lv2/img28.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546586103&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Lv2/img06.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546586103&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Afew-X-Beams-Orange-Koi/Lv2/img16.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546586103&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel-Diablo', 'Asics', 'Ronnie Fieg Volcano 2.0', 175, 'This Ronnie Fieg designed ASICS Gel Diablo "Volcano 2.0" was the Kith founder’s first ever design for the Gel Diablo — a silhouette which first dropped in 1995. An alternate take on Fieg’s classic 2013 Gel Lyte 5 "Volcano,"" the shoe features a premium nubuck, sport mesh, and pigskin suede construction with a Parchment, Volcano, Ash Pink, and navy colorway. It initially dropped as a 500 pair KITHstrike in early April 2017 before 500 additional pairs were released alongside the Ronnie Fieg x Gel Lyte 3 "Volcano 2.0" in the ‘Volcano 2.0’ pack.', 2017, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Images/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Images/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Lv2/img18.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Images/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Lv2/img14.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Images/asics-gel-diablo-ronnie-fieg-volcano-2-0_TruView/Lv2/img08.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel-Lyte Speed', 'Asics', 'Ubiq Cool Breeze', 140, 'The UBIQ x ASICS Gel Lyte Speed “Cool Breeze” is the latest collaboration between both brands that is designed perfectly for the summer time.This UBIQ x ASICS Gel Lyte Speed “Cool Breeze” is inspired by the positive and refreshing vibes we all experience during the summer months. The clear Blue skies and rejuvenating feeling when we step into the cool waters of the ocean served as the muse when developing this project. Every time you slip on a pair of the “Cool Breeze,” they want you to remember the tranquil feeling of seeing Crystal Blue skies, and touching the Teal Blue waters.', 2015, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549855968&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Lv2/img21.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549855968&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Lv2/img15.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549855968&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-Speed-Ubiq-Cool-Breeze_TruView/Lv2/img06.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549855968&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Onitsuka Tiger Colorado 85 Bait Bruce Lee', 'Asics', 'Yellow/Black', 160, 'Californian streetwear retailer Bait teamed up with Onitsuka Tiger for this tribute to Bruce Lee to celebrate what would have been his 75th birthday in 2015. Sporting a colorway inspired by the yellow and black jumpsuit and Onitsuka Tiger Corsairs that Lee wore in Game of Death, the shoe features a premium nubuck upper with leather tiger stripes, a leather lining, and a speckled sole. It also comes with Bruce Lee branding on the tongue, his signature on the yellow lace aglets, embroidered Onitsuka Tiger and Bruce Lee kickman logos on the heel, and custom insoles with a Bruce Lee 75th-anniversary logo.', 2018, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Images/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856040&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Images/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Lv2/img29.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856040&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Images/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Lv2/img22.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856040&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Images/Asics-Onitsuka-Tiger-Colorado-85-Bait-Bruce-Lee/Lv2/img09.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856040&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel-Saga Diamond Supply Co x Ronnie Fieg "Tiffany" Black', 'Asics', 'Black/Aqua', 165, '"Bringing the East and West coasts together, KITH-founder Ronnie Fieg and Diamond Supply Co. have teamed up with ASICS to reimagine both the Gel Saga silhouettes with Diamond’s iconic “Diamond Blue” hue. Utilizing the previously mentioned shade about its pigskin suede toe, lace eyestay and striped branding, the Gel Saga offering is equipped with blackened leather sprucing up its heel and interior lining."', 2015, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img12.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-saga-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img06.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel Lyte V', 'Adidas', 'Aqua/White-Grey', 175, 'Bringing the East and West coasts together, KITH-founder Ronnie Fieg and Diamond Supply Co. have teamed up with ASICS to reimagine Gel Lyte V silhouettes with Diamond’s iconic “Diamond Blue” hue. Its Gel Lyte V dips the large majority of its microperforated pigskin suede upper in the refreshing blue hue while metallic silver fiberglass material, leather and hits of 3M add to the aesthetic appeal.', 2015, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856028&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img19.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856028&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img15.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856028&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Images/asics-gel-lyte-v-diamond-supply-co-x-ronnie-fieg-tiffany_TruView/Lv2/img05.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549856028&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Gel Lyte 3 Titolo "Papercut"', 'Asics', 'Black/Red-White', 160, 'Titolo is back with a brand new collaborative effort atop the ever-classic Asics Gel Lyte III. Named the “Papercut”, this isn’t an homage to the stingingly painful cuts on your fingertips, but instead references the art of Scherenschnitt, or paper cutting. In an homage to the Switzerland boutique’s Zurich shop, this Gel Lyte III references the intricate pattern on the ceiling of the store with a unique insole while the black and white floral pattern extends to the neoprene mesh and side panel striping. The premium black base is in an effort to continue the premium Tiger branding that was recently introduced.', 2015, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546679336&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Lv2/img30.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546679336&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Lv2/img17.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546679336&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Images/Asics-Gel-Lyte-III-Titolo-Papercut/Lv2/img06.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546679336&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Retro 11 ', 'Jordan', 'Concord', 220, 'Jordan Brand is reaching harder than MJ on Space Jam for the sneaker of the year crown by releasing the Jordan 11 Retro Concord (2018). This Iconic Jordan 11 colorway is showcasing a white upper with black accents, white midsole, and a freezing cold translucent sole. These sneakers released in December 2018 and retailed for $220. Revisit the dominant legacy MJ left behind.', 2018, 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/805882_2.jpg', 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/805882_4.jpg', 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/805882_1.jpg', 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/805882_3.jpg');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Retro 3', 'Jordan', 'Black Cement', 200, 'One of the most anticipated releases of 2018, the Air Jordan 3 Retro OG marked the first time original "Nike Air" branding was featured on the "Black Cement" AJ 3 since it''s 2001 retro. Jordan stuck to the mantra of “if it aint broke, don’t fix it,” on these, staying true to the OG with a black-based leather upper with cement grey, fire red, and white accents, finished off by the iconic elephant print detailing.', 2018, 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/803229_01.jpg', 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/803229_02.jpg', 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/803229_03.jpg', 'https://www.flightclub.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1600x1140/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/8/0/803229_04.jpg');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Retro 6', 'Jordan', 'Black/Infrared', 200, 'Make sure your head isn’t in the beam while trying to grab the Jordan 6 Retro Black Infrared (2019). This AJ6 come with a black upper, black midsole plus red accents, and a translucent sole. These sneakers released in February 2019 and retailed for $200.', 2019, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Images/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549058088&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Images/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Lv2/img28.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549058088&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Images/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Lv2/img19.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549058088&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Images/Air-Jordan-6-Retro-Black-Infrared-2019/Lv2/img08.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1549058088&w=1300');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Travis Scott Air Jordan 4 Retro', 'Jordan', 'University Blue/Black-Varsity', 225, 'The only way to describe the Travis Scott Air Jordan 4 Retros properly would be to use the rappers own adlib: la flame. These Jordan 4s were made in collaboration with rapper, Travis Scott and nicknamed the “Cactus Jack” edition. Similar in design to the infamous Eminem pair, these feature a lighter shade of blue suede on the upper. Black accents, a red liner, paint splatter detailing, a white midsole and “Cactus Jack” branding on the back heel tab finish things off for this pair. These dropped in June of 2018 for $225 and came exclusively in men’s sizes. If you’re a fan of Travis Scott and the AJ 4, this pair is another must-have.', 2019, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Lv2/img26.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Lv2/img10.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Travis-Scott-Cactus-Jack/Lv2/img17.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=1300');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Jordan 4 Retro UNDFTD', 'Jordan', 'Olive-oiled Suede-Flight Satin Undftd', 17500, 'The Undefeated Air Jordan 4 originally debuted in 2005 and was limited to only 72 pairs. Each pair was given out to friends and family and never actually released at retail. This was the first time Jordan Brand teamed up for a collaboration with a third party.', 2005, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Lv2/img12.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-UNDFTD_TruView/Lv2/img06.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1538080256&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Jordan 4 Retro Black Cement', 'Jordan', 'Black/Fire Red-Cement Grey', 160, 'Because this is an older release, deadstock pairs may come with yellowed wings due to natural aging', 2012, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551048119&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Lv2/img20.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551048119&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Lv2/img15.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551048119&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Images/Air-Jordan-4-Retro-Black-Cement-2012_TruView/Lv2/img07.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1551048119&w=2200');

INSERT INTO shoes(shoe_model, brand, colorway, price, description, year_released, image_1_url, image_2_url, image_3_url, image_4_url)
VALUES('Jordan 3 Retro', 'Jordan', 'White/Cement Grey-Fire Red', 150, 'The Nike Air Jordan III Retro White/Cement from 2011 was a long overdue release. By 2011, the White Cement Jordan III had sat in the vault at Nike since the 2003 release. Which meant, for most sneakerheads, you had already burned through at least a pair or two of the iconic Jordan 3 sneaker. This variation of the White Cement Jordan III Retro was the first time it became a problem that the “Nike Air” wasn’t on the heel of the shoe. Purists might have been offish with the 2003 release but it became mainstream to complain about the Jumpman on the heel thanks to platforms like Twitter and Instagram. Outside of sneaker enthusiasts, however, it didn’t matter because the memories of the 1988 Dunk Contest, and MJ taking off from the free throw line still conjured up memories for Chicago Bulls and Michael Jordan fans. The 2011 Jordan III sold well initially, selling out in most places rather quickly but restocks meant getting your hands on a pair wasn’t impossible, especially considering the latte January release that meant plenty of holiday money burning a hole in the pockets of sneaker enthusiasts. In terms of quality and availability, the 2011 Air Jordan Retro 3 White Cement might be the lowest of all the original colorway Jordan 3s but it will always have a mass appeal that most sneakers will never have thanks to Michael Jordan.', 2011, 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Images/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Lv2/img01.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546584106&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Images/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Lv2/img28.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546584106&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Images/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Lv2/img16.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546584106&w=2200', 'https://stockx-360.imgix.net/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Images/Air-Jordan-3-Retro-White-Cement-2011/Lv2/img09.jpg?auto=format,compress&q=90&updated_at=1546584106&w=2200');


